messages.content:
"The Provider shall implement and maintain technical and organizational measures that meet or exceed the ISO/IEC 27001 standard, including:
• Encryption of all Personal Data in transit using TLS 1.2 or higher and at rest using AES‑256;
• Regular vulnerability assessments and penetration testing at least annually;
• A documented breach‑notification procedure that requires the Provider to inform the Customer within 24 hours of becoming aware of a breach, providing details of the incident, affected data, and remedial actions taken.
The Provider shall cooperate fully with the Customer in responding to any breach, including providing forensic reports and assistance with regulatory notifications."
